node.text:
Who’s down for free stuff?😏 I did a collab with @dhar.mann 🔥to celebrate we’re giving away 2 iPhone 12’s and 2 Apple laptop’s! To win:

1. Like this photo 
2. Tag a friend in the comments
3. Share this on your story

You must be following @dhar.mann & I to win (we’ll check)! Each comment is a separate entry but must tag different people for it to count! 
Will list winners on this post by Friday. Good luck! 🎉
